OL,3,CTeenage boy, 17, charged with murder
OL,4,Cfollowing stabbing of man
OL,6,FA teenage boy has been charged in
OL,7,Fconnection with a fatal stabbing near
OL,8,FReading.
OL,10,FPolice were called to an alleyway in
OL,11,FLower Earley on Saturday (23 May).
OL,13,FMuhammad Noor Majid Butt, 20, was
OL,14,Ffound with injuries and was taken to
OL,15,Fhospital, where he later died.
OL,17,FHis next of kin are being supported by
OL,18,Fspecially trained family liaison
OL,19,Fofficers.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
