OL,3,CTeenage boy, 17, charged with murder
OL,4,Cfollowing stabbing of man
OL,6,FA 17-year-old boy, from Reading, has
OL,7,Fbeen charged with one count each of
OL,8,Fmurder and possession of an offensive
OL,9,Fweapon.
OL,11,FThe teenager is due to appear at
OL,12,FReading Magistrates Court on Thursday
OL,13,F(28 May).
OL,15,FTwo teenage boys, from the town, who
OL,16,Fwere arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,17,Fon Wednesday (27 May) both remain in
OL,18,Fcustody.
